PN,31301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,FDeep-fried food will be banned from
OL,7,Fschool menus while cakes, pizza,
OL,8,Fsausage rolls and other unhealthy
OL,9,Flunches will be limited as part of a
OL,10,Fsweeping standards overhaul aimed at
OL,11,Ftackling childhood obesity and tooth
OL,12,Fdecay.
OL,14,FDesserts like ice cream and waffles,
OL,15,Fand baked goods such as puddings and
OL,16,Fcakes, will be served only once a week
OL,17,Fand need to contain at least 50% fruit
OL,18,Funder new rules proposed by the
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will promote the
OL,7,Fplans "supporting better health for
OL,8,Fthe future" on a visit to Greater
OL,9,FManchester on Monday.
OL,11,FSchools will no longer be able to
OL,12,Foffer unhealthy "grab and go" options
OL,13,Fsuch as sausage rolls and pizza every
OL,14,Fday, and deep-fried food will be
OL,15,Feliminated from menus entirely as part
OL,16,Fof the plan.
OL,26,@oD@GOUpD@KO]tD@QOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
