OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,FEach school will be asked to publish
OL,7,Ftheir menus online to help boost
OL,8,Fcompliance as part of the proposals,
OL,9,Fwhich are being put to a nine-week
OL,10,Fconsultation starting on Monday.
OL,12,FFruit will need to be served for the
OL,13,Fmajority of the week instead of sugary
OL,14,Ftreats, with sample menus including
OL,15,Fmains such as cottage pie with root-
OL,16,Fand-veg mash, Mexican-style burritos,
OL,17,Fjerk chicken with rice and peas and
OL,18,Fspaghetti bolognese.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,FEach dish must be accompanied by one
OL,7,For more portions of vegetables and
OL,8,Fsalad, and sides cooked using fat or
OL,9,Foil, such as chips and hash browns,
OL,10,Fare to be served no more than twice a
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FDespite the proposed ban on deep-fried
OL,14,Ffood, breadcrumb-coated or batter-
OL,15,Fcoated options like fish and chips
OL,16,Fwill also still be permitted once a
OL,17,Fweek under the plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
