PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,FThe first new standards since 2014
OL,7,Fwill aim to increase fibre intake by
OL,8,Fensuring more fruit, vegetables and
OL,9,Fwholegrains are on offer and have been
OL,10,Fdeveloped with help from health
OL,11,Fexperts and nutritionists.
OL,13,FBacked by actress Dame Emma Thompson,
OL,14,FLeon co-founder Henry Dimbleby and
OL,15,Fchef Tom Kerridge, they will apply to
OL,16,Fall breakfasts and lunches served in
OL,17,Fschools, the Department for Education
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
