FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,FAround one in three children are
OL,7,Fleaving primary school overweight or
OL,8,Fobese, while tooth decay is the
OL,9,Fleading cause of hospital admissions
OL,10,Ffor youngsters aged five to nine.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister, ahead of a visit
OL,13,Fto a school breakfast club in Greater
OL,14,FManchester, said: "We're improving the
OL,15,Fquality of food served in schools so
OL,16,Fparents can count on their children
OL,17,Fgetting healthy meals.
OL,19,F"This is about easing the cost of
OL,20,Fliving today and supporting better
OL,21,Fhealth for the future."
OL,26,@vD@SOU{D@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
