SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fsaid the proposals were "the most
OL,8,Fambitious overhaul of school food in a
OL,9,Fgeneration" and were "long overdue".
