PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,F"Every child deserves to have
OL,7,Fdelicious, nutritious food at school
OL,8,Fthat gives them the energy to
OL,9,Fconcentrate, learn and thrive ` meals
OL,10,Fthat children will actually recognise
OL,11,Fand enjoy, backed by robust compliance
OL,12,Fso that good standards on paper become
OL,13,Fgood food on the plate," she said.
OL,15,FChef and campaigner Jamie Oliver said
OL,16,Fschool food was "the UK's most
OL,17,Fimportant restaurant chain" and offers
OL,18,Fa "massive opportunity to improve
OL,19,Fhealth at scale".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@XO]xD@QOUyD@[O]zD@COU{D@PO]
