CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776089466
OL,3,CSchool menu shake up to see deep-fried
OL,4,Cfoods banned and sweet treats cut down
OL,6,F"My Good School Food Awards prove that
OL,7,Fworld-class meals are possible right
OL,8,Fnow, and every child deserves that
OL,9,Fsame quality," he said.
OL,11,F"So, I'm delighted this Government is
OL,12,Fnow updating and enforcing these
OL,13,Fstandards."
